# Spartan UI + Tailwind CSS

## UI Stack

- **Components**: Spartan UI (headless, CDK-based primitives)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS utility classes
- **NO Angular Material** — never import `@angular/material/*`

## Theming

Use CSS custom properties consumed via Tailwind config:

```typescript
// tailwind.config.js
theme: {
  extend: {
    colors: {
      colla: {
        primary: 'var(--colla-primary)',
        secondary: 'var(--colla-secondary)',
      }
    }
  }
}

// Usage in templates
<button class="bg-colla-primary text-white">Button</button>
```

## Responsive Design

- **Mobile-first**: Base styles = mobile, `lg:` prefix = desktop
- **Breakpoints**: sm (640px), md (768px), lg (1024px), xl (1280px)
- **Touch targets**: min 44x44px on mobile (`min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px]`)
- **Tables**: Spartan Table on >=lg, card layout on <lg
- **Forms**: Single column <md, multi-column >=md
- **Sidebar**: Hidden <lg (Spartan Sheet drawer), visible >=lg

## Component Patterns

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD — Spartan + Tailwind
import { HlmButtonDirective } from '@spartan-ng/ui-button-helm';

@Component({
  standalone: true,
  imports: [HlmButtonDirective],
  template: `<button hlmBtn variant="outline" class="min-h-[44px]">Cerca</button>`
})

// ❌ BAD — Angular Material
import { MatButtonModule } from '@angular/material/button';
```

## Spartan Components

- **Buttons**: `hlmBtn` directive
- **Tables**: `HlmTable` + CDK Table
- **Forms**: `HlmInput`, `HlmSelect`, `HlmLabel`
- **Badges**: `HlmBadge`
- **Modals**: `HlmDialog`
- **Drawers**: `HlmSheet`
- **Toasts**: `HlmSonner`
- **Icons**: `HlmIcon` (lucide-angular)

## Styling Rules

- All visual styling via Tailwind utilities
- No component-level SCSS except complex animations
- Use `@apply` sparingly (prefer inline utilities)
- Dynamic colors: `[style.backgroundColor]` binding or `bg-[var(--custom)]`
